comments.body:
Get an item status
```
item.send(:get_clancy, url: "itemstatus/v1/32101103768097")
```

Cancel an item request looking for the request id in the item status
```
body = { "requests": [{ "request_type": "CANCEL", "barcode": "32101103768097", "stop": 'MQ', request_id: "32101103768097-22101008595068-1649085248
"}]}
response = item.send(:post_clancy, url: "circrequests/v1", body: body.to_json)
```
@christinach I updated the typos.  Thanks for catching those...
closed by https://github.com/pulibrary/orangelight/pull/2913
